></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>칭찬과 격려의 댓글은 작성자에게 큰 힘이 됩니다 :)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">onChange</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>onChangeCommentInput<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Register</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alert</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>opacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">등록</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Register</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>headers에 토큰을 보내 로그인상태인 사람만 댓글추가 가능.<br>\n성공적으로 POST 됐다면 setCommentList를 해서 댓글state 변경</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"